(http://campaignmonitor.com)

Complete List of Template Tags
==============================

Making content editable

    Single Line: &lt;singleline&gt;&lt;/singleline&gt;
    Multi Line: &lt;multiline&gt;&lt;/multiline&gt;
    Image: &lt;img editable=&quot;true&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;
    Repeater: &lt;repeater&gt;
    Layout: &lt;layout&gt;
    Table of Contents: &lt;tableofcontents&gt;
    Repeater Title: &lt;repeatertitle&gt;&lt;/repeatertitle&gt;
    Disabling Link Tracking and Image Importing

Quick Links

    Web Version: &lt;webversion&gt;
    Forward to a Friend: &lt;forwardtoafriend&gt;
    Unsubscribe: &lt;unsubscribe&gt;
    Preference Center: &lt;preferences&gt;
    Facebook Like: &lt;fblike&gt;
    Tweet: &lt;tweet&gt;

Dates

    Current day (Number): &lt;currentday&gt;
    Current day (Name): &lt;currentdayname&gt;
    Current month (Number): &lt;currentmonth&gt;
    Current month (Name): &lt;currentmonthname&gt;
    Current year (Number): &lt;currentyear&gt;

Personalization

    First name: [firstname,fallback=text]
    Last name: [lastname,fallback=text]
    Full name: [fullname,fallback=text]
    Email Address: [email]
    Custom fields
